    title: "Marine Transit Insurance: Understanding Cargo Insurance Clauses",
    excerpt: "Learn how the Institute Cargo Clauses (A, B, and C) define the boundaries of cargo and transit risk coverage.",
    category: "Business Risk",
    readTime: "8 min read",
    date: "March 05, 2026",
    author: { name: "Siya Thaku", role: "Transit & Warehouse Risk Consultant" },
